# Netlify redirects (bundled into dist/ so manual/drag-drop deploys get them too).
# Proxy API + health to the Tencent Cloud backend, keeping the browser same-origin
# so the custom X-PAYMENT header needs no CORS preflight. Order matters: these must
# precede the SPA fallback.
/api/*    https://api.optle.hanjun.kim/api/:splat    200
/health   https://api.optle.hanjun.kim/health        200

# SPA fallback.
/*        /index.html                                 200
